    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble meets all pre-specified acceptance criteria for the three QoIs under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors achieve required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the single-condition validation is sufficient given the well-characterized ASTM F1717 protocol and the supporting experimental evidence from two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is judged adequate for the Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence classification.",
